<H1>    Design Petri Net    Model</H1>
<H1><FONT color=mediumblue>    Factors to Consider</FONT></H1>
</CENTER>

<UL><UL><UL> <UL><UL>
  <LI><FONT size=5>traffic flows in each 
          way/direction;</FONT>
          <LI><FONT size=5>the percentage of the traffic going through, left 
          turn, or right left;</FONT>
          <LI><FONT size=5>speed limit;</FONT>
          <LI><FONT size=5>average starting time for the cars;</FONT>
          <LI><FONT size=5>average stopping time for the cars;</FONT>
          <LI><FONT size=5>the weather/seasons; the possibility of the drivers 
          violating the rules;</FONT>
          <LI><FONT size=5>have pedestrian lights or 
not.</FONT></LI></UL></UL></UL></UL></UL>

